WEBVTT

00:01:58.893 --> 00:02:02.810
Then he put his hand on my shoulder
and he looked me in the eyes,

00:02:02.834 --> 00:02:04.060
and he said,

00:02:04.933 --> 00:02:07.952
"That's what the communists
and the Jews want you to do

00:02:07.976 --> 00:02:09.345
to keep you docile."

00:02:11.330 --> 00:02:12.512
I was 14 years old,

00:02:12.536 --> 00:02:15.410
I'd been trading baseball cards
and watching "Happy Days" --

00:02:15.434 --> 00:02:17.208
I didn't really know what a Jew was.

00:02:17.232 --> 00:02:19.002
(Laughter)

00:02:19.026 --> 00:02:20.177
It's true.

00:02:20.201 --> 00:02:24.176
And the only communist that I knew
was the bad Russian guy

00:02:24.200 --> 00:02:26.068
in my favorite Rocky movie.

00:02:26.092 --> 00:02:28.723
(Laughter)

00:02:28.747 --> 00:02:30.978
And since I'm here
baring my soul with you,